Titolo: Stories Untold (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Stories Untold is an episodic horror adventure-puzzle video game developed by No Code and published by Devolver Digital. Written and directed by Jon McKellan, the game was released on 27 February 2017 for macOS and Microsoft Windows, for the Nintendo Switch in January 2020 and for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One in October 2020. It is a mix of adventure game genres, including text-based adventure, first-person exploration, and puzzle solving, and is themed after technology from the 1980s.The game consists of four episodes, each of them an adventure and horror game. The first, notably, is a remastered version of The House Abandon, a shorter adventure game released as free-to-play in August 2016.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
